      "role": "user",
      "content": "Wait, what? Your transmission is garbled. I'm getting some weird telemetry feedback from your comms array. Just ignore the noise and focus on the sonar readings. You certain those mineral readings aren't real? If they are, we need to lock in the coordinates immediately. Check your sensor integrity and confirm.",
